These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, badminton, parkour, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: jet-ski, train, van, trike
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left of the person driving the train##1
3. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the van is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
5. the person who's sport is skiing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Sport   | skiing | badminton | biathlon | parkour |
| Transport        | jet-ski | train   | trike | van    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, surfing, climbing, skiing
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, lemonade, fanta
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person who's sport is skiing##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
3. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
6. the person drinking almond-milk is the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Sport   | climbing | ice-hockey  | surfing  | skiing |
| Beverage   | fanta    | almond-milk | lemonade | coffee    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
House: ranch-style, tower, wooden, craftsman
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, black, blue, orange
1. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
2. the wooden house is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes orange is on the left or right of the tower house##3
4. the person who likes orange is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
5. the person who likes brown is in an odd position##4
6. the tower house is on the right of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| House          | craftsman | wooden | tower    | ranch-style      |
| Color   | blue        | orange     | brown | black |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, balloon-flower, dahlia, aconite
There are 4 different favourite colors: lilac, black, apricot, red
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who likes lilac and the person who likes red##2
2. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsmarigold##1
3. the person who likes apricot is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes black is on the left of the person who likes red##1
5. the person who likes black is on the right of the person who growsmarigold##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Flower         | aconite | marigold | balloon-flower | dahlia |
| Color   | apricot       | lilac   | black    | red  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, january, april, july
The people use 4 different means of transport: skateboard, jet-ski, train, bus
1. the person who's birthday is in april is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the person driving the train is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
4. the person who's birthday is in january is on the far left##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is in an odd position##4
6. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | january  | november    | april   | july       |
| Transport   | skateboard | bus | train | jet-ski |

