.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, sudoku, rock-climbing, filmmaking
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, black, chestnut, azure
1. the person who likes black is in an even position##4
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who likes green is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
5. the person who likes chestnut is on the left or right of the person who likes green##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing      | sudoku | filmmaking | board-games |
| Color   | azure | black     | green  | chestnut  |

