.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, lizard, hedgehog, pony
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, amber, mauve, fuchsia
1. the person who likes fuchsia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who likes mauve is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the owner of the pony is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
4. the person who likes fuchsia is the owner of the ferret##1
5. the owner of the pony is on the left or right of the person who likes brown##3
6. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes brown##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Pet   | ferret | pony | hedgehog | lizard    |
| Color     | fuchsia | mauve  | brown     | amber |

