.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, marigold, bellflower, daisy
City: liverpool, hamburg, marseilles, prague
1. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
2. the person who growsdaisy is in an odd position##4
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person who growsdaisy##3
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
5. the person who growsamaryllis is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growsmarigold##2
6. the person traveling to hamburg is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person traveling to marseilles##2
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Flower   | marigold | amaryllis      | daisy | bellflower |
| City   | liverpool  | prague | hamburg    | marseilles            |

