.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, photographer, scientist, chef
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, nigerian, dutch
1. the scientist is on the left or right of the designer##3
2. the designer is on the right of the photographer##1
3. the argentine is between the egyptian and the scientist##2
4. the argentine is in an odd position##4
5. the scientist is the nigerian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Job   | chef | photographer   | designer | scientist |
| Nationality    | dutch     | egyptian | argentine     | nigerian  |

