.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, indonesian, french, egyptian
City: london, marseilles, boston, hamburg
1. the argentine is the person traveling to hamburg##1
2. the person traveling to london is on the right of the argentine##1
3. the person traveling to hamburg is between the person traveling to london and the french##2
4. the argentine is in an odd position##4
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
6. the indonesian is on the left or right of the person traveling to marseilles##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Nationality      | indonesian       | french   | argentine | egyptian |
| City   | boston | marseilles | hamburg        | london    |

