.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, doctor, project-manager, analyst
There are 4 different nationalities: german, american, mexican, analyst-polo
1. the german is in an even position##4
2. the mexican is on the right of the paramedic##1
3. the mexican is on the left of the analyst-polo##1
4. the analyst-polo is on the left of the project-manager##1
5. the doctor is on the left or right of the project-manager##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job   | paramedic   | analyst   | doctor      | project-manager      |
| Nationality      | american | mexican | analyst-polo | german |

