.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, motorbike, ship, subway
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: azalea, daisy, zinnia, marigold
1. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
2. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the motorbike is in an even position##4
4. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
5. the person driving the ship is between the person who growsdaisy and the person who growszinnia##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Transport          | subway | motorbike  | ship  | van |
| Flower   | marigold  | zinnia | azalea | daisy   |

