.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, 7up, sprite, lemonade
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, chaman, bongani, davidoff
1. the chaman-smoker is in an odd position##4
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
4. the person drinking 7up is in an odd position##4
5. the chaman-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |     4     |
| Beverage   | 7up | fanta | sprite | lemonade  |
| Cigar     | chaman   | bluemaster  | davidoff  | bongani |

