.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, juice, tea, coffee
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, bridge, canasta
1. the person playing bridge is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
4. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
6. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |   3    |      4       |
| Beverage   | tea | coffee | lemonade | juice |
| Game           | canasta     | mah-jongg     | bridge   | billiard         |

