.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, ebony, apricot, light-blue
There 4 different types of food: watermelon, strawberry, grapefruit, grapes
1. the person who likes blue is between the person eating watermelon and the person who likes ebony##2
2. the person who likes apricot is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1
5. the person eating grapes is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Color   | light-blue | ebony         | blue   | apricot |
| Food   | grapefruit    | strawberry | grapes | watermelon   |

