.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, polish, canadian, dutch
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, jet-ski, ship
1. the person driving the ship is the canadian##1
2. the person driving the jet-ski is the nigerian##1
3. the person driving the taxi is the dutch##1
4. the canadian is on the left or right of the dutch##3
5. the nigerian is in an even position##4
6. the canadian is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Nationality   | polish | nigerian | canadian    | dutch |
| Transport   | snowmobile   | jet-ski  | ship | taxi     |

