.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, indie, disco, hip-hop
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, lavender, ivory, blue
1. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of disco is in an even position##4
3. the person who likes lavender is the fan of disco##1
4. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the person who likes lavender##3
5. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes blue and the person who likes ivory##2
6. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes blue##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Music-Genre         | hip-hop   | disco | rock | indie    |
| Color   | ivory | lavender  | blue     | blood-red |

