.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
City: boston, paris, venice, san-francisco
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, aristoff, baccarat, dunhill
1. the aristoff-smoker is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to boston##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the baccarat-smoker is in an even position##4
7. the prince-smoker is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| City   | san-francisco | boston    | venice       | paris |
| Cigar       | aristoff  | baccarat | dunhill | prince  |

