City: san-francisco, prague, liverpool, paris
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
2. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to san-francisco##3
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
4. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
5. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | october | may | november  | march |
| City     | san-francisco      | liverpool       | prague | paris     |

