.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, milk, water
There 4 different types of food: onion, carrot, pineapple, pepper
1. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person eating onion##3
3. the person eating carrot is between the person drinking sprite and the person eating onion##2
4. the person drinking 7up is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person drinking water##1
6. the person eating pineapple is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Beverage         | sprite | milk   | water | 7up |
| Food   | pepper          | carrot | onion         | pineapple  |

 